descp2: Determines whether CUDA headers and libraries are added to the build. If set to `None` (default), this value is automatically determined based on the existence of `.cu` or `.cuh` in `sources`. Set it to True` to force CUDA headers and libraries to be included.

Determines whether CUDA headers and libraries are added to the build. If set to `None` (default), this value is automatically determined based on the existence of `.cu` or `.cuh` in `sources`. Set it to True` to force CUDA headers and libraries to be included.
